        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Andreas Dilger",
          "email": "andreas.dilger@intel.com",
          "date": "2017-04-07 21:55:50.000000000",
          "tz": -360
        },
        "subject": "LU-8998 llapi: remove llapi_layout_comp_use_id()",
        "message": "LU-8998 llapi: remove llapi_layout_comp_use_id()\n\nThe llapi_layout_comp_use_id() function is mostly the same as\nllapi_layout_comp_use(), combine the two into a single function.\n\nAdd LLAPI_LAYOUT_COMP_USE_PREV to the llapi_layout_comp_use() API,\nand test for same in llapi_layout_test.c.\n\nUse LCME_ID_INVAL instead of comparing component ID to 0 directly.\n\nDefine LCME_FL_NOT_ID to make it clear that this flag is already\nused instead of just a comment at the lcme_id declaration.  Rename\nLCME_ID_NONE to LCME_ID_NOT_ID to clarify that this is a flag.\n\nReserve 4095 component IDs for future use.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I771aea48d323adc78432cb024f219d43ca6cab07\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/pfl"
    }
  },
